DdAY 6



=> Day 6 Summary <=
	===================
	mainly cashirku waxa uu diiradda saaray OOP.
1. waa maxay OOP?
	-> waa in la abuuro object kaasoo ka koobnaan kara data iyo method.
2. why we need OOP?
	-> waxay kuu sahlaysaa in code kaaga nodqo mid fudud oo aan lahayn repeat ama soo noqnoqod fara badan.

	OOP marka lajoogo waxaa muhim ah in la ogaado labo shey : => Class , => object.
3. what is class?
	- class is a group of variables, constructors, methods, blocks etc.
	marka aan class abuurayno waxaan adeegsnaynaa keyword "calass" kadina waxa la raaciya magaca classka u yeelanayo.
	=> syntax:
	class ClassName
  	 {
      	    // variables, constructors,
           // method declarations
   	 } .
	=>
==> class waa templete of an object.
==> object is an instance of class .
==> calss is logical construct. while object is phycial reality.
	object waxa uu qaataa space in memory.
==> what is instance variable.
	- variable inside the object.
==> si aan u abuurno object waxaan adeegsanaynaa keyword "new".
==> objects ka waxaa ukala baxaan 3 qayb:
	- state
	- identity
	- behavior.
==> instance variable: waa variable ku dhex jira objectiga.
==> dot operator: waxay waxay isku xireysa magaca objectiga iyo variableska ku dehx jra objectigaas.
==> A constructor waxa uu qeexayaa wxayaabaha dhacaya markii objecti classka ka tirsan la abuuro.
==> this keyword: marka aan rano inaan soo access gareno object classka ka tirsan waxaan u baahan nahay inaan istcimaalo "this" keyword.